---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="404 | Yuimi Lab" description="这个页面迷路了。">
  <section class="not-found">
    <div class="not-found-copy">
      <p class="section-kicker">Lost Page</p>
      <h1>404</h1>
      <p>这张便签好像被风吹走了。回到首页，我们重新翻开下一页。</p>
      <a class="back-link" href="/">← 回到首页</a>
    </div>
    <figure class="not-found-visual">
      <img src="/assets/legacy/404.jpg" alt="404 illustration" />
    </figure>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
